A^2 + B^2 + C^2 - 2AB -2AC - 2BC =
(A + B + C)^2 - 4AB - 4AC - 4BC =
(A + B + C - 2 \sqrt{AB + AC + BC}) (A + B + C + 2 \sqrt{AB + AC + BC})
